  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2599480/extras/d0d39bbbc3d3bb5f753aa6f03a99d93f.webp?t=1728997977\" width=600 height=45 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2599480/extras/042f318325c9dd2381b30e132e2b28ca.poster.avif?t=1728997977\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2599480/extras/042f318325c9dd2381b30e132e2b28ca.webm?t=1728997977\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2599480/extras/042f318325c9dd2381b30e132e2b28ca.mp4?t=1728997977\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Russian roulette game you can play with your friends!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>2-person, 4-person lobbies can be create.</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Or you can fight against other players online with the matching system.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Emotes</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>We have 8 emotes! You can share your feelings with the other players!</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2599480/extras/bcac32b8193001a57286524319b2f8d3.poster.avif?t=1728997977\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2599480/extras/bcac32b8193001a57286524319b2f8d3.webm?t=1728997977\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2599480/extras/bcac32b8193001a57286524319b2f8d3.mp4?t=1728997977\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Musics</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>We have songs that we have prepared specifically for our game!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2599480/extras/aee6612140b89a3e8eba10bd120be966.poster.avif?t=1728997977\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2599480/extras/aee6612140b89a3e8eba10bd120be966.webm?t=1728997977\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2599480/extras/aee6612140b89a3e8eba10bd120be966.mp4?t=1728997977\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Items</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>There are items in the game that can strategically put you ahead. Each round, an equal number of items are randomly given to everyone.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2599480/extras/9d974b518698ce223c009233a461965c.poster.avif?t=1728997977\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2599480/extras/9d974b518698ce223c009233a461965c.webm?t=1728997977\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2599480/extras/9d974b518698ce223c009233a461965c.mp4?t=1728997977\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>More will come later!</strong></p>",
